name: Decimated T-90 For Ukraine
description:
A 3D-model of a T-90 tank—similar to many of those used by invading Russian ground forces—is textured with z-flighting flags of Ukraine and Russia and decimated.

75% of sales will be donated to KT1DWnLiUkNtAQDErXxudFEH63JC6mqg3HEx in support of Ukraine. More info: https://nftbiker.xyz/event/supportukraine
